Privacy Policy

Last Updated: January 11, 2026

Your privacy is important to us. This app is designed to keep your personal journaling safe and private.

1. Data Collection
We do not collect, store, or share any personal information. All journal entries and app data remain on your device only.

2. Use of Your Data
Since all data stays local, we do not access, view, or process your journal entries in any way.

3. Third-Party Services
This app does not use analytics, advertising, or any third-party services that track your activity.

4. Security
Your data is stored on your device. We recommend using your deviceâ€™s built-in security features to keep your journal safe (e.g., device passcode, biometric locks).

5. Changes to This Policy
If we ever change how your data is handled, we will update this privacy policy and notify users through app updates.

6. Contact
